metadata.name: Aandra
metadata.description:
**Mutant Aquatic Warriors Club (MAWC)** is a community-driven AI-Generated NFT project featuring 3333 unique NFTs.

With MAWC, you no longer have to worry about flipping NFTs to earn cryptocurrency
-simply HODL and earn up to 20% in Shardeum (SHM) tokens from the fees generated by our upcoming NFT Marketplace,
[Shardible](https://shardible.io/).

Shardible is a predominant, end-to-end NFT marketplace built on Shardeum blockchain that offers comprehensive support for all your NFT needs, whether you're a collector, artist, or developer.

With MAWC, you'll own a unique piece of digital art and earn rewards simply by holding onto your NFT.

Join the Mutant Aquatic Warriors Club today and become part of our thriving community!
